title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should display in data set dialog
OB: While in the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result is that the output parameter does not display in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Open the data set dialog. 
2. Execute a query that has an output parameter. 
3. Check if the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
